{"word":"λίψ","slug":"λίψ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λίψ1</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:λείβω'><el>λείβω</el></a>, because it brought wet\n<p/><i>the SW. wind</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>Africus</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/> <hr/> <el><b>λίψ2</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:λείβω'><el>λείβω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> and <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:λιβάς'><el>λιβάς</el></a> or <a href='S:λίβος'><el>λίβος</el></a> being used as <a href='S:nominative'>nom.</a>\n<p/><i>a stream</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>: <i>a draught</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}